content:
I've been looking into code signing stuff for macOS nightlies...looks like we can get our developer program fee waived because we're a nonprofit!

https://developer.apple.com/news/?id=01032018a
we should probably apply for a DUNS number sooner rather than later bc they take 30 business days to go through https://www.dnb.com/duns/get-a-duns.html

I've made a note to look into the DUNS number. This did get me thinking, now that we have a fixed url for nightly releases we can get around code signing issues by providing a curl command in the getting started doc.
